📁 Project 1: Responsive Contact Form with Validation
📝 Title: Responsive Contact Form with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript Validation
📋 Description:
A fully responsive contact form built using HTML, styled with CSS Flexbox and Grid, and enhanced with JavaScript for real-time input validation. This project demonstrates the integration of form structure, design, and client-side validation logic.

💡 Features:
Responsive layout using Flexbox & CSS Grid

Custom form styling and design

JavaScript validation for required fields

Email format check before submission

Alerts and error feedback for a better user experience

🚀 How to Use:
Clone or download the repository

Open index.html in your browser

Fill out the contact form and test the validation logic

🛠️ Tech Stack:
HTML5

CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid, Media Queries)

JavaScript (vanilla DOM scripting)
